snippet.title: The Supper: New Blood Wishlist Trailer
snippet.description:
Your first guest is here...and something tells me they’ll never leave this motel...
A crazy, hilarious adventure game for those who enjoy dark humor, bizarre puzzles, and exquisite food!
WISHLIST NOW!
